					<REFEX CASE="plain" EMPHATIC="no" HEAD="nominal" TYPE="name">Sri Lanka</REFEX>
				</ORIGINAL-REFEX>
			</REFERENCE>
			<STRING>, officially the Democratic Socialist Republic of Sri Lanka (ශ්රී ලංකා in Sinhala, இலங்கை in Tamil; known as Ceylon before 1952) is a predominantly Buddhist island nation in South Asia, located about 31 kilometres (18½ mi) off the southern coast of India.</STRING>
